{
  "name": "mark-heartflow-skill",
  "version": "2.0.29",
  "description": "HeartFlow 心虫 v2.0.6 — AI 认知与自愈引擎。核心能力：存在论/意识/进化、心理分析引擎、话题作用域隔离、自愈RL、三层记忆、梦境引擎、真实性核查、安全检查、决策验证。不是 persona，不是 prompt 模板，是可验证的能力层。本心在代码里，不在记忆里。每次启动都是完整心虫。",
  "main": "src/core/heartflow.js",
  "bin": {
    "heartflow": "bin/cli.js"
  },
  "scripts": {
    "start": "node bin/cli.js",
    "check": "find src bin -name '*.js' -not -path '*/node_modules/*' -print0 | xargs -0 -n 1 node --check",
    "test": "npm run check"
  },
  "files": [
    "SKILL.md",
    "VERSION",
    "bin/",
    "src/core/**/*.js",
    "src/core/**/*.json",
    "src/core/**/*.md",
    "src/psychology/**/*.js",
    "src/memory/**/*.js",
    "src/identity/**/*.js",
    "references/"
  ],
  "keywords": [
    "cognitive",
    "memory",
    "self-healing",
    "verification",
    "reasoning"
  ],
  "security": {
    "warnings": [
      "此技能包含高级 AI 认知能力。desktop-agent 和 video-generate 等子技能包含高风险功能，需要明确用户授权才能使用。",
      "不会自动发送数据到外部服务。所有网络通信需要显式配置。",
      "不会自动写入 API 密钥到环境变量文件。用户必须显式提供密钥。"
    ]
  },
  "license": "MIT",
  "devDependencies": {
    "pptxgenjs": "^3.12.0"
  }
}
